# Consumer My Profile | Set Primary Shipping Address

## **Executive Summary**
This feature allows customers to easily set a **primary shipping address** within their account profile. The primary address will be used by default during checkout, ensuring a smoother purchase experience. Clear visual indicators (e.g., "Primary Address" tag) and feedback (success toast) will confirm successful updates.
## Business Objective
*   Allow customers to designate one shipping address as their **primary address**.
*   Provide clear and intuitive UI to manage multiple shipping addresses.
*   Improve efficiency and reduce errors during checkout by defaulting to the primary address.
## **Scope of Solution**
*   Customers can view all their saved addresses in the "Shipping Address" section of their account profile.
*   Each address is displayed as a card with actions.
*   A **“Set as Primary Address”** link is shown on all non-primary address cards.
*   Once selected:
    *   The chosen address becomes the primary.
    *   The "Set as Primary Address" link is hidden from the selected card.
    *   A "Primary Address" tag is displayed.
    *   A success toast confirms the update.
*   The system automatically updates the **Primary Address field** with the chosen address name.
