## **Nonfunctional Requirements**

| **Category** | **Requirement Description** | **Priority** |
| ---| ---| --- |
| **Performance Requirements** | Primary address update should complete in less than 2 seconds. | High |
| **Security Requirements** | Only authenticated customers can make address changes. | High |
| **Usability Requirements** | Provide clear UI feedback with a success message and visual tag when primary address updates. | Medium |
| **Reliability Requirements** | Only one address should ever be set as the primary address at any given time. | High |
| **Scalability Requirements** | Support customers having multiple saved addresses without issues. | High |
